Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>com.puppycrawl.tools</groupId>
  <artifactId>checkstyle</artifactId>
  <version>8.21</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'com.puppycrawl.tools:checkstyle:jar:8.21'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="com.puppycrawl.tools" name="checkstyle" rev="8.21">
  <artifact name="checkstyle" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='com.puppycrawl.tools', module='checkstyle', version='8.21')
)

Gradle/Grails

compile 'com.puppycrawl.tools:checkstyle:8.21'

Scala SBT

libraryDependencies += "com.puppycrawl.tools" % "checkstyle" % "8.21"

Leiningen

[com.puppycrawl.tools/checkstyle "8.21"]
